     <div class="post-97 page type-page status-publish hentry" id="post-97">
      <h1>
       Chairman Message
      </h1>
      <div class="entry-content">
       <p>
        First of all, I would like to thank God almighty for the success I have reached and achieved. Success needs work and sacrifices with God’s grace and blessings.
       </p>
       <p>
        We live in an extraordinary time. Every change around us does not necessarily bring about growth, but presents us with an opportunity to rediscover, re-energize and reinvent ourselves. Twenty five years ago I have started with a small company, and making such a group with different kinds of businesses, gave me the faith, belief, and courage that continuous hard work will result in a bigger, better and stronger future.
       </p>
       <p>
        We don’t work for money; we work for name and reputation.
       </p>
       <p>
        Finally, as it is a family business, I hope sons and staffs of Al Alaa CMC continue to achieve the same goals, producing and generating success in all kinds of businesses they interfere in. On the other hand, I hereby renew my own and my Group’s commitment to achieve excellence as a standing criteria for all our services that we provide to our valued customers. We also renew our pledge towards ethical and professional principles which enables us to acquire the recognition and respect of whoever dealt with us.
       </p>
       <p>
        In ALL OF THE ABOVE, WE ARE, AND AIM TO CONTINUE TO BE, SECOND TO NONE…
       </p>
       <p>
        Fayez Ali Heeba
        <br />
        Chairman
       </p>
      </div>
      <!-- .entry-content -->
